long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Adds a button that cycles through the list of audible tabs.

Pin the extension's icon to your extension bar, then click on it to quickly switch to the browser tabs that are currently playing audio.
